title: Anaida - Nazuk Nazuk (1995)
description:
Anaida is Eurasian . She is an Indian performer, actor, director, producer, pop and playback singer, multi-linguist, advertising conceptualizer, creative exponent of the fine arts, writer/poet and painter. Anaida has been an integral part of the Indian Entertainment Industry for more than 18 years.
In the early 1990s, She was one of India's first pop singers. Since then she has launched 10 albums and a score of singles, in Hindi, English, Tamil, Malayalam, Punjabi, Greek, and Arabic. She sings in 11 languages. She has acted in Hindi movies and guest appearances in numerous television shows.
